      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、芽衣さん、おかえりなさい\n何かいいことでもあったんですか？",
      "startTime": 9.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 6.122698625
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、実は芽衣ね～\n今度雑誌の企画に参加することになったの！",
      "startTime": 16,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』\nっていうんだけどね",
      "startTime": 21.4801588817,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "お誕生日プレゼントのかわりに\nアイドルがやってみたいことを叶えちゃおう",
      "startTime": 25.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "っていうバースデー企画なんだって！\nもう、今から楽しみだよ～！",
      "startTime": 31.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "わ～！　やってみたいことを叶えてくれるなんて\n素敵な企画ですね。いいな～",
      "startTime": 40.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ！　すみれちゃんも一緒に参加しない？",
      "startTime": 44.0157828171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "え？　私もですか？",
      "startTime": 47.5924493472,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　さっきの打ち合わせで\n他に二人参加出来ることになったんだ～！",
      "startTime": 52.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "仲良しなメンバーと一緒の方が、華やかになるし\n企画も盛り上がりそうだから～って！　どうかな？",
      "startTime": 59.8911695692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、参加は、してみたいんですけど～\n仲良しなメンバーって、私でいいんでしょうか……？",
      "startTime": 69.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "だって芽衣とすみれちゃん、仲良しでしょ？\n同じ星見プロの仲間だし！",
      "startTime": 78,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "それに芽衣、みんな仲良しで大好きだから\n悩み始めると決まらなそうで～",
      "startTime": 84.9999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、なんだか芽衣さんらしいですね\n分かりました、せっかくのお誘いですし参加しますね！",
      "startTime": 92.5666656494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣さんのお誕生日企画\n仲良しメンバーとして、しっかり盛り上げてみせます！",
      "startTime": 99.5666656494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "やったー！　すみれちゃん、よろしくね！\nじゃあ、もう一人は～",
      "startTime": 107.7666656494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "二人とも、何話してるの？",
      "startTime": 111.9681874592,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 65.14485690000527,
          "startTime": 112.0333323161
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "渚ちゃんにけって～～～～い！",
      "startTime": 114.671339321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "渚さん、よろしくお願いします！\n一緒に目一杯盛り上げましょうねっ",
      "startTime": 121.7333323161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "え？　えっと、よろしくね……？",
      "startTime": 124.5324958324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
