      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "あ、この欄ですね。ふむふむ……\n『ドーナツのお風呂に入りたい』",
      "startTime": 158.9999989827,
      "sfxList": []
