      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "大好きなドーナツと、この前行って楽しかった温泉\n二つを思い切ってくっつけてみたの！　どうかなー？",
      "startTime": 169.6999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、楽しそうではあるんだけど、なんていうか……\nね、すみれちゃん",
